    • Method Detail

      • analyseRecording

        java.util.List<Classification> analyseRecording(RecordingEntity recordingEntity)
        Analyse a recording given its unique recording ID. The analyser will load all SensorDataEntity in the database which have the id as a foreign key. Each of those data streams is analysed and critical points/ points of interest are stored in Classification instances.
        Parameters:
        recordingEntity - Recording which is analysed.
        Returns:
        a list of Classification instances.
